    "description": "Nexum Backend API Collection\n\n## Authentication\nMost endpoints require JWT Bearer token authentication. Use the Login endpoint to obtain tokens.\n\n## Error Responses\nAll error responses follow a standard format with `error.code`, `error.message`, and `error.displayType` fields.",
